data.description: Nestled in the heart of untouched beauty lies an extraordinary opportunity to own 5 acres of sprawling, flat land, awaiting your vision and dreams. With 5 acres at your disposal, there's ample room to bring your imagination to life. But why stop at 5 acres when you can expand your horizons even further? For those with grander aspirations, the opportunity to acquire two additional adjacent parcels presents itself, offering a total of 15 acres of contiguous land. (Additional Lands sold separately).
